  In a message dated 10/30/06 8:14:21 AM, benthin(-at-)prodigy.net writes:

  I keep a CLEAR tube about 6 ft long in the bus for this- tube tends to
  bend around in the tank and suck air- the trick is to feed it in as you
  BLOW through the other end until you hear bubbles-push in further
  (seeing that bubbles still sound-then suck until you see the gas and
  stick your finger over the end and place into receptacle.

